text: Bianca Dancose-Giambattisto is a Canadian artistic gymnast. She was a member of the Canadian women's national gymnastics team from 2010 to 2012 and competed in college gymnastics for the University of Florida's Florida Gators gymnastics team. == References == Category:1994 births Category:Canadian female artistic gymnasts Category:Florida Gators women's gymnasts Category:Sportspeople from Montreal Category:Living people
